00:25:36.400 --> 00:25:37.920
Take a good look

00:25:38.920 --> 00:25:40.240
at this city.

00:25:42.079 --> 00:25:44.839
Compared to the nonsense
Yang Wenyuan told you,

00:25:45.079 --> 00:25:47.039
look at what we built.

00:25:47.480 --> 00:25:48.599
Which path actually worked?

00:25:49.200 --> 00:25:51.640
Back when you went out
causing trouble with him,

00:25:51.839 --> 00:25:54.400
I could've crushed you
without leaving a trace.

00:25:57.079 --> 00:25:58.880
What did I ever do to deserve this?

00:26:00.799 --> 00:26:01.640
Well, Wu.

00:26:02.559 --> 00:26:05.799
It's not that I wanted
to push you forward.

00:26:06.359 --> 00:26:08.279
I was trying to save us.

00:26:08.640 --> 00:26:10.880
There are things
you just can't do anymore.

00:26:10.880 --> 00:26:12.160
I still have a son.

00:26:12.160 --> 00:26:14.960
You're scared? But I'm not.

00:26:15.440 --> 00:26:17.480
I didn't do that dirty business.

00:26:18.039 --> 00:26:19.880
You gave the orders.

00:26:20.400 --> 00:26:22.039
(Contract, Xu Peng)
You signed all the papers.

00:26:23.039 --> 00:26:23.880
Go on.

00:26:26.680 --> 00:26:28.920
No. You forced me to sign.

00:26:29.319 --> 00:26:30.839
You kept threatening me with Shuqin.

00:26:31.279 --> 00:26:32.680
But now Shuqin is gone.

00:26:32.690 --> 00:26:35.290
Worst case, I'll drag you down with me.
I'm not afraid of you anymore.

00:26:36.000 --> 00:26:37.680
No. No. No.

00:26:39.400 --> 00:26:40.559
You have to fear me.

00:26:41.279 --> 00:26:42.559
All of you have to fear me.

00:26:43.279 --> 00:26:44.759
You must fear me.

00:26:46.000 --> 00:26:49.960
Hongyue, your girls' lives
are in my hands.

00:26:51.160 --> 00:26:52.119
You're afraid of me.

00:26:55.160 --> 00:26:55.960
Xu Peng,

00:26:58.480 --> 00:27:01.799
