♪How could one bear to shed it?♪

00:37:57.700 --> 00:38:03.900
♪Sufferer,
hate is a road with no return♪

00:38:03.900 --> 00:38:06.660
♪There's nothing at the end♪

00:38:06.660 --> 00:38:10.260
♪Cause and effect trade roles♪

00:38:10.980 --> 00:38:13.140
♪Unable to love♪

00:38:13.140 --> 00:38:17.420
♪Yet still leap into pavilions in air♪

00:38:17.420 --> 00:38:19.340
♪Unable to let go♪

00:38:19.340 --> 00:38:23.980
♪Still asking why♪

