00:39:41.820 --> 00:39:43.700
♪One glance back♪

00:39:43.700 --> 00:39:48.220
♪Who is not a guest to feast and die♪

00:39:48.260 --> 00:39:50.540
♪Only then do we know at the start♪

00:39:50.880 --> 00:39:52.039
(From this moment on,)

00:39:53.260 --> 00:39:55.159
(I won't let the satan
pull my strings anymore.)

00:39:57.159 --> 00:40:00.000
(I want to live like Yang Wenyuan did.)

00:40:00.679 --> 00:40:01.880
(Like Qu Meng did.)

00:40:03.440 --> 00:40:04.639
(I want to live with backbone)

00:40:06.480 --> 00:40:07.920
(and die with dignity.)

00:40:07.920 --> 00:40:09.500
♪One word from me♪

00:40:09.860 --> 00:40:14.140
♪Yet I don't know how to say it to you♪

00:40:14.140 --> 00:40:20.780
♪Look at those lanterns,
the years locked us in♪

00:40:20.780 --> 00:40:31.420
♪Hear the joyous song rise,
the human heart tastes bitter♪

00:40:35.880 --> 00:40:36.760
Slow down.

00:40:46.400 --> 00:40:48.159
Why look for Xu Zhiyang's contact?

00:40:49.280 --> 00:40:51.039
Winning him over helps us too.

00:40:53.480 --> 00:40:55.000
What's the next move?

00:40:57.199 --> 00:40:58.440
Before contacting Xu Zhiyang,

00:40:59.440 --> 00:41:01.280
we should probably talk
to Wu Feifei first.

00:41:06.599 --> 00:41:08.159
This is finally coming to an end.

00:41:09.360 --> 00:41:10.119
End?

00:41:12.900 --> 00:41:15.480
Are there still other crimes
hidden inside the International Club?

00:41:16.400 --> 00:41:18.000
What's the real truth?

00:41:18.000 --> 00:41:19.480
Wu Feifei, don't you want to know?

00:41:20.519 --> 00:41:22.360
Gao Feng, I happened to pass by
your old place

00:41:22.360 --> 00:41:23.960
after dinner earlier today.

00:41:25.599 --> 00:41:27.039
I saw your mother

00:41:28.000 --> 00:41:29.380
playing mahjong with the neighbors.

00:41:30.559 --> 00:41:32.239
Muke Bar has reopened as well.

00:41:33.200 --> 00:41:35.100
After everything you and Long Yu
went through,

00:41:36.320 --> 00:41:38.119
you should understand each other
better now.

00:41:40.039 --> 00:41:41.639
You should be able to live well.

00:41:45.840 --> 00:41:49.440
Don't you think your life is better now?

00:41:50.440 --> 00:41:52.690
I think living well right now
matters more than anything.

00:41:53.199 --> 00:41:54.119
Stop lying to yourself.

00:41:55.039 --> 00:41:55.880
We're the same.

00:41:58.260 --> 00:41:59.280
We can't go back anymore.

00:41:59.660 --> 00:42:02.079
Have you ever thought about
when things went out of control?

00:42:02.560 --> 00:42:04.320
Was it when your mom
tried to ram the statue

00:42:04.519 --> 00:42:06.000
and led me to look into my own mother?

00:42:06.100 --> 00:42:07.920
Or when your mom chose
not to call the police

00:42:08.079 --> 00:42:09.519
and died alone in that attic?

00:42:10.199 --> 00:42:12.480
Or before any of this happened,

00:42:12.760 --> 00:42:14.480
when fate brought us together?

00:42:15.440 --> 00:42:16.039
Listen.

00:42:16.039 --> 00:42:18.079
If I'd never stepping into
this mess with you,

00:42:19.400 --> 00:42:21.199
I'd still be that happy,

00:42:21.199 --> 00:42:23.199
obedient daughter.

00:42:24.159 --> 00:42:26.000
My dad would still be a good father.

00:42:26.760 --> 00:42:29.480
None of this would have anything
to do with me.

00:42:32.480 --> 00:42:33.760
You were the catalyst,

00:42:33.760 --> 00:42:34.719
you know?

00:42:35.639 --> 00:42:36.840
Sometimes I wonder,

00:42:37.400 --> 00:42:38.440
if I hadn't gone

00:42:40.000 --> 00:42:41.599
drinking with you that day,

00:42:43.360 --> 00:42:44.519
would everything

00:42:44.519 --> 00:42:46.039
be different now?

00:42:47.800 --> 00:42:49.000
Sometimes I really wish

00:42:49.880 --> 00:42:51.039
we had never met.

00:43:00.840 --> 00:43:03.119
It's now basically confirmed

00:43:03.320 --> 00:43:04.400
that back in the 1990s,

00:43:04.440 --> 00:43:08.000
the person responsible
for the illegal sex trade

00:43:08.000 --> 00:43:10.039
at the International Club was Xu Peng.

00:43:10.239 --> 00:43:12.599
Among the surveillance tapes
submitted by Xu Zhiyang,

00:43:12.800 --> 00:43:15.639
one clearly shows

00:43:15.639 --> 00:43:18.079
how Xu Peng killed Qu Meng.

00:43:18.400 --> 00:43:20.079
After forensic verification,

00:43:20.719 --> 00:43:22.679
